Injector/Double Punch/Manterror:



Injector shut Ramhorn's chest plate and looked to Scorponok.  "Back off!  
We'll deal with this Maximal dog!  Go help Quickstrike!" he yelled, firing 
two stinger missiles off at Ramulus.

Manterror fired two ion disks off at some trees, cutting the trunks and 
sendin them down towards Archangel and Striker.

Double Punch nodded, stomping on Dark Mouse's head with a chuckle, picking 
her, putting her over his shoulder, and running into the Pred base.
